     node
-----------------

a runtime enviornment that let you run javascript outside the browser build on chroms vs engine

---------express--------

express is lite weight framwork for node js 
it prvides tools to handle http request routing middlware and more


mvc architecture - model view controller
it is a software desingned pattern that suprates a application into 3 inter connected components


model = it manages data logic and rules of the application eg-database schema

view = here view handles user interface and presentasion layer - eg- frontend,html,css templates

controller = it act as an intermediary proccessing user input and updating model and view  eg- routing request ,user requesting input form 


step 1 = user intract wit the view eg- click on the button to fetch the data

step-2 = controller recives the request and decided what to do

step 3 = controller communicate with the model to fetch the data

step 4 = model update the data and snd the results back

step 5 =  controller passes the data to the view

step 6 = view render the updated ui



