                     context api
------------------------------------------------------
  
context api is a builin react feature that enables vomponents to share data and state across the entire application components

it avoids props drilling


1 create context 
it isa function used to create a context object


2. provider 
this is the component that wraps your app and broadcast the data


3.use context
this is the reciver hook used by any nested components to access the data